  "1744390": {
    "name": "Shop Tycoon Demo",
    "steam_appid": 1744390,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744390/extras/7de9adb4bec99f1443049b07689c1f35.avif?t=1769787808\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >信息</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Shop Tycoon》是一款商店模拟经营游戏。从一家小店起步，逐步打造一座拥有停车场、员工办公室和庞大车队的大型商场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744390/extras/4b848026e8db91d1abd288bbc2ec3526.poster.avif?t=1769787808\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744390/extras/4b848026e8db91d1abd288bbc2ec3526.webm?t=1769787808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744390/extras/4b848026e8db91d1abd288bbc2ec3526.mp4?t=1769787808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Shop Tycoon》既可以当作没有竞争压力的轻松休闲游戏来玩，也可以当作残酷无情的商店模拟器来玩——一群“Bandytko”正等着骗走你的钱，甚至伤害你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744390/extras/13d49c80a04ea8e95b4f8bf3f8e0ca5d.avif?t=1769787808\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造超市、游戏店、成人用品店，或经营高品质的波兰伏特加。修建停车场，吸引越来越多的顾客，让你的收入不断增长。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744390/extras/5867d504b29991f7022a384d451f1789.poster.avif?t=1769787808\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744390/extras/5867d504b29991f7022a384d451f1789.webm?t=1769787808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744390/extras/5867d504b29991f7022a384d451f1789.mp4?t=1769787808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扩充你的车队以提升商店的营业额。你还可以雇佣经理来管理车队和员工。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744390/extras/f2934ddf41d8feeba0f0bf82b2c284eb.poster.avif?t=1769787808\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744390/extras/f2934ddf41d8feeba0f0bf82b2c284eb.webm?t=1769787808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744390/extras/f2934ddf41d8feeba0f0bf82b2c284eb.mp4?t=1769787808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造公交车停车场，吸引更多顾客来到你的精品店，增加收入。此外，你还可以升级游戏中的公交车和其他元素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744390/extras/31bea942f26cb0ba5f96bb6ca92d0c05.poster.avif?t=1769787808\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744390/extras/31bea942f26cb0ba5f96bb6ca92d0c05.webm?t=1769787808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744390/extras/31bea942f26cb0ba5f96bb6ca92d0c05.mp4?t=1769787808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一开始你必须亲力亲为（就像独立工作室 Airem 一样），但随着时间推移，你可以雇佣员工，比如负责执行各种工作流程的经理（他们会检查商品、保质期等），或在店里抓小偷的保安。让你的业务实现自动化，赚更多的钱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744390/extras/fe6f00f1e28a74d9b494a3addae1a3c8.poster.avif?t=1769787808\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744390/extras/fe6f00f1e28a74d9b494a3addae1a3c8.webm?t=1769787808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744390/extras/fe6f00f1e28a74d9b494a3addae1a3c8.mp4?t=1769787808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在全球扩张你的连锁店，在互联网、电视或广播上为商店做宣传。组织促销活动，并与互联网/电视/广播广告联动。当你遇到麻烦时，可以通过多种方式获得贷款……或者永久关店！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744390/extras/3c867d84995334e2008089d4c2415887.avif?t=1769787808\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为顾客提供多种便利设施，例如移动支付、购物篮、会员卡等等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744390/extras/611f47c52317a3f5fcf28d96167dd341.avif?t=1769787808\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理员工：他们可能生病或休假；如果他想加薪就把这个混蛋开了（[剧透]xD [/剧透]）……或者如果他值得，就给他涨薪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1744390/extras/e7b81e6a1dce26c73f33acfaa0848875.avif?t=1769787808\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >优点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >名人</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建立你自己的商店</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高分系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 个结局</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >29 种语言 + 白俄罗斯语</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自定义标志（商店、车队等）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam 成就</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam 云存档</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持手柄、鼠标，或仅用键盘游玩</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卖伏特加（你甚至可以卖给孩子）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >注意卫生与卫生防疫检查</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让你的企业免于破产，为你的商店打造一个成功且长久的品牌</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >轻松的音乐与音效</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >缺点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你必须每月支付租金、税费等：-/</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bandytko 帮派让生活更艰难等 :-( </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完整游戏还有很多其他功能未在此列出，因为描述有字符限制。</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 阿拉伯语, 保加利亚语, 繁体中文, 简体中文, 捷克语, 丹麦语, 芬兰语, 希腊语, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 荷兰语, 日语, 韩语, 挪威语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语, 罗马尼亚语, 瑞典语, 泰语, 土耳其语, 乌克兰语, 越南语, 匈牙利语",
